description: Westpay AB engages in the provision of transaction and payment solutions. The company is headquartered in Upplands Vaesby, Stockholm and currently employs 36 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2007-10-26. The Company’s offering includes card terminals, equipment for sale systems, cash management solutions, self-service kiosks, as well as other products. The company also offers such services, as helpdesk and support, rental and repair, among others. The Company’s solutions are applicable within various industries, such as retail, hotels and restaurants and the retail banking sector. The firm is active in five main market areas: The Nordic countries, Europe, Africa, South- and South East Asia, as well as Australia.
name: Westpay AB
